Worshipper (7)
- The Worshipper has the ability to use 3 types of prayers.
- 1.Heavenly Incantation- can respawn a person immediately.
- 2.Earthly Incantation- can reduce respawn phases by 4 for the team members who are respawning.
- 3.Demonic Incantation- can increase respawn phases by 2 for an enemy.
- Each Incantation takes 2 phases to cast except the Heavenly incantation which is immediate upon use.
- Post-Night Action, each incantation can be used once and only one incantation can be used per night. 
- The target affected will be informed. Respawn times cannot be extended beyond 6 phases. Any attempts to do this will silently fail.
- The incantations are returned on death.
- Respawns in 6 phases.
